cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.NI

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper proposes an upgraded electro-magnetic side-channel attack and a protection system against it, which falls under the domain of cryptography and security. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed system is based on deep learning and character recognition, which suggests the involvement of machine learning techniques. 
3. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The character recognition component of the proposed system involves computer vision and pattern recognition techniques. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper mentions the use of software-defined radio and graphics processing unit architectures, which are related to systems and control. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The proposed solution can be deployed onto existing information systems, which suggests a possible connection to networking and internet architecture.
